openapi: 3.0.3
info:
  title: Callbacks

paths:

              requestBody:

                  application/json:
                    schema:
                      $ref: '#/components/schemas/CallbackRequest'
                required: true
              responses:
                '200':
                  description: ''
                '400':

                  content:
                    text/plain:
                      schema:
                        type: string
        my_reusable_callback:

components:

    TriggerRequest:

    CallbackRequest:

        answer:
          type: string
  callbacks:

          operationId: deleteReusable_callback

              content:
                text/plain:

                    type: string
